you doing here, Spike?

34
00:02:25,102 --> 00:02:26,831
- Harmony, please.
<i>- [Gunn] This is Spike?</i>

35
00:02:26,937 --> 00:02:28,598
<i>- The</i> Spike?
- Wait a minute, who's...

36
