42
00:02:47,024 --> 00:02:50,391
<i>Well, yeah.</i>
<i>Who here isn't?</i>

43
00:02:50,494 --> 00:02:53,395
Besides him and him
and her and...

44
00:02:54,498 --> 00:02:56,762
