45
00:03:12,416 --> 00:03:14,316
Bugger.

46
00:04:11,308 --> 00:04:14,766
What... What's
happened to me?

47
00:04:17,281 --> 00:04:21,513
<i>Well, I'm no doctor,</i>
<i>but I think you're a ghost.</i>

48
00:04:21,619 --> 00:04:24,144
I'm no...
I'm no bloody ghost.

49
00:04:24,254 --> 00:04:26,688
Hey, you're the one
sticking out of a desk, pal.

50
00:04:26,790 --> 00:04:30,385
