Scanner girl?

87
00:06:27,244 --> 00:06:31,237
I'm Fred. I head up
Wolfram and Hart's Science Department.

88
00:06:31,348 --> 00:06:34,806
Wolfram and Hart? Heard of that.
Thought it was a law firm.

89
00:06:34,918 --> 00:06:37,182
It is, among other things.

90
00:06:37,287 --> 00:06:39,915
Also heard they represent
the worst evil in the universe.

91
00:06:40,023 --> 00:06:44,119
