consistent with spiritual entities...

94
00:06:50,467 --> 00:06:52,367
but there's no
ectoplasmic matrix.

95
00:06:52,469 --> 00:06:56,462
- Meaning?
- Ectoplasm is what makes
ghosts visible to the human eye.

96
00:06:56,573 --> 00:07:00,031
If he's a ghost, technically
we shouldn't be able to see him.

97
00:07:00,144 --> 00:07:02,977
And I'm detecting
brain wave activity.

98
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:05,173
On Spike? Huh.
That is weird.

99
00:07:05,282 --> 00:07:09,150
Also, ghosts generally
absorb light and heat energy...

100
00:07:09,253 --> 00:07:12,188
