- A little tip, Spike.

157
00:10:25,816 --> 00:10:27,784
Try not to talk about
things you don't understand.

158
00:10:27,884 --> 00:10:30,717
I'm not the prat here.
I know you, Angel.

159
00:10:30,821 --> 00:10:35,087
What do you think you're doing? You made
some devil's bargain to take over this company.

160
00:10:35,192 --> 00:10:38,753
