you and yours are getting digested.

162
00:10:41,865 --> 00:10:44,163
- Not gonna happen.
- What, you think you're in control here?

163
00:10:44,267 --> 00:10:47,430
Guess again, mate.
You're no more in control than I am.

164
00:10:47,537 --> 00:10:50,700
Except I'm not gonna bloody stand for it,
while you're just a blind...

165
00:10:50,807 --> 00:10:53,708
- Grox'lar beast.
- What?

166
00:10:57,481 --> 00:11:00,541
[Growls]

167
00:11:05,322 --> 00:11:07,290
Oh, brilliant.

168
00:11:20,237 --> 00:11:22,364
[Bones Cracking]

169
00:11:26,410 --> 00:11:29,811
[Exhales] Okay. Somebody wanna
tell me how a Grox'lar beast...

170
00:11:29,913 --> 00:11:31,813
got past Security?

171
00:11:31,915 --> 00:11:34,440
- I don't have time for this.
<i>- [Spike] Of course not.</i>

172
00:11:34,551 --> 00:11:37,816
Man's gotta stay focused on
profit margins and power lunches.

173
00:11:37,921 --> 00:11:39,889
- Angel...
- Yeah, Spike, I've got a business to run.

174
00:11:39,990 --> 00:11:42,322
