- Get 'em to stop eating baby heads.

180
00:12:02,946 --> 00:12:04,937
Oh, so that's good.

181
00:12:06,450 --> 00:12:08,850
Oh, so this...
this is bad.

182
00:12:08,952 --> 00:12:13,150
No, actually the Grox'lar clan respects someone
who takes a strong opening position.

183
00:12:13,256 --> 00:12:15,918
