from every dimension.

185
00:12:18,061 --> 00:12:20,325
<i>Probably should've briefed</i>
<i>you about the Grox'lar...</i>

186
00:12:20,430 --> 00:12:23,126
but we got a little
sidetracked.

187
00:12:24,701 --> 00:12:27,829
Plus, I've been implementing our
reforms, mostly staff overhaul.

188
00:12:27,938 --> 00:12:30,202
