in the past two days.

189
00:12:30,307 --> 00:12:32,002
- How's that goin'?
- As expected.

190
00:12:32,109 --> 00:12:34,805
Anger, tears,
venomous death threats.

191
00:12:34,911 --> 00:12:38,312
<i>Listen, I know I was</i>
<i>a little crabby before.</i>

192
00:12:38,415 --> 00:12:41,714
I mean, hello.
A little awkward seeing you at my work.

193
00:12:41,818 --> 00:12:46,653
But if... if you want to talk or something,
you know, about us or...

194
00:12:49,126 --> 00:12:51,720
Okay, too soon.

195
00:12:51,828 --> 00:12:53,921
I understand.

196
00:12:54,030 --> 00:12:56,157
Slayer-loving freak.

197
00:12:56,299 --> 00:12:58,665
Caught an associate
we laid off...

198
00:12:58,768 --> 00:13:01,532
tryin' to smuggle this
out of the Voodoo Division.

199
00:13:02,839 --> 00:13:04,864
It's a nice likeness.

200
00:13:06,076 --> 00:13:08,510
<i>This placejust</i>
<i>goes on and on, doesn't it?</i>

201
00:13:08,612 --> 00:13:10,477
Like a ruddy
theme park attraction.

202
00:13:10,580 --> 00:13:14,414
- I'm in a meeting, Spike.
- Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't care.

203
00:13:14,518 --> 00:13:16,748
<i>We're rufflin'a lot of</i>
<i>dangerous feathers out there.</i>

