- Grave-robbing.

211
00:13:33,103 --> 00:13:36,834
<i>Listen, I know you fellows are in charge now,</i>
<i>and you're doin'a bang-upjob.</i>

212
00:13:36,940 --> 00:13:38,669
<i>I'm with you 110%.</i>

213
00:13:38,775 --> 00:13:41,369
